Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:49.80,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Cause lately I couldn't find these answers to live by instead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:52.22,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Some will call it giving up
